Nepal Friends of the Commonwealth (UK)
This friendship Seat was dedicated on 3rd September 2000
in loving memory of the lat
LT Gareth Evans and SGT Balram Rar
of the 69th Gurkha Field Squadron
who lost their lives in service during NATO peacekeeping
operations in Kosovo on 21st June 1999"„
ýOCTOBER 5th. 1988
ON OCT. 5th. 1938 IN HANKOW. CHINA
DAVID AND WINIFRED GUNN WERE MARRIED
AND TODAY WITH GREAT JOY
THEY CELEBRATE FIFTY GOLDEN YEARS

OCTOBER 5TH 1993
EMERALD WEDDING ANNIVERSARY
FIVE MORE HAPPY YEARS"„
